  "response": "Email to SMS gateways have varying levels of service and pricing in India. Here's a general overview:\n\n1. Free Services:\n- Some telecom operators provide limited free email-to-SMS services\n- Certain websites offer free email-to-SMS conversion\n- Google Voice has some free SMS relay options\n\n2. Paid Services:\n- Most reliable and consistent email-to-SMS services require payment\n- Charges typically depend on:\n  - Number of SMS\n  - Destination telecom network\n  - Message length\n\n3. Common Providers:\n- Twilio\n- MSG91\n- Way2SMS\n- TextLocal\n- SendSMS.co.in\n\n4. Factors Affecting Cost:\n- Telecom operator charges\n- Service provider's markup\n- SMS volume\n- Message type (transactional/promotional)\n\n5. Limitations:\n- Some free services have message count restrictions\n- Delivery not always guaranteed\n- Potential delay in message transmission\n\nRecommendation:\n- Check with specific service providers\n- Compare pricing and features\n- Read user reviews before selecting\n\nFor precise, current pricing, it's best to directly contact SMS gateway service providers in India.",
